data.description: New and Improved Price!! Make this house your home! This property offers three bedrooms and two bathrooms, featuring original, refinished hardwood flooring in the living area, hallway, and both guest bedrooms. The kitchen boasts an abundance of cabinets, granite countertops, a raised bar for additional seating, and a stunning lighting package. The stainless steel side-by-side refrigerator is included.The master suite is generously sized and includes its own fireplace, perfect for enjoying romantic evenings or chilly nights. The master bathroom has been elegantly updated with a large shower and an impressive walk-in closet. The roof was replaced approximately three years ago.The house is updated with refrigerated air, double-paned windows, and wood faux blinds. The backyard offers ample space, providing enough room for a pool and more.
